{"type":"message","id":"07e08d2c","parentId":"a62b1745","timestamp":"2026-03-25T17:06:40.698Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Addressing the user's request**\n\nThe user asked me to open and play the song \"Risk It All\" on YouTube. They’ve made similar requests before, but unfortunately, I can't control an external browser directly without certain configurations. I did attempt to open the browser previously, but ran into errors. Still, I can search YouTube for \"Risk It All\" and share a link to a video for the user. I’ll clarify that I can’t play audio directly in the chat.**Providing YouTube links**\n\nI can share direct YouTube links to \"Risk It All,\" including the official video by Bruno Mars at https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lY5V4hSLWY8. There are also tracks from his album, \"The Romantic,\" and other artists like Chase McDaniel with \"Risk It All.\" I should list the top options with notes about what's official and guide the user on how to play them directly. I won't overuse tools, but if they want, I can fetch the page or search for more video results.**Clarifying video links**\n\nI've got results for Bruno Mars already. The user asked to play a song, but I can't do that directly due to tool limitations. Instead, I'll share some direct YouTube links for them to click on. I’m thinking of providing three options, like the official music video: \"Bruno Mars - Risk It All\" at https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lY5V4hSLWY8. There’s some uncertainty about whether that video is from his album \"The Romantic,\" so I need to confirm that detail before presenting everything clearly.**Confirming video accuracy**\n\nI need to be careful with the details about Bruno Mars and his song \"Risk It All.\" It seems there might be some incorrect information about the album release date. I should only provide valid video links. I can present the official video at https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rPpusObDFSo, which was mentioned in previous search results. There's also the ID lY5V4hSLWY8 for another video related to \"The Romantic.\" I'll ensure the recommendations I give are accurate and trustworthy.**Responding to the user in Indonesian**\n\n[[reply_to_current]] I cannot play music directly here due to limitations in the environment. However, you can click one of the YouTube links below to start playing \"Risk It All\":  \n\n- Official video Bruno Mars - Risk It All: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rPpusObDFSo  \n- Bruno Mars - Risk It All (official video alternative): https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BF2_ipR1OI0  \n- Risk It All (another version/album): https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lY5V4hSLWY8  \n\nIf you'd like me to search for other versions or set a reminder, feel free to ask!","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Saya tidak bisa memutar musik langsung di sini karena keterbatasan lingkungan OpenClaw. Namun, kamu bisa klik salah satu link YouTube berikut untuk mulai memutar lagu “Risk It All”:\n\n- Bruno Mars - Risk It All [Official Music Video]: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rPpusObDFSo\n- Risk It All - Bruno Mars (Video lain): https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BF2_ipR1OI0\n- Bruno Mars - Risk It All [Video alternatif]: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lY5V4hSLWY8\n\nIngin saya cari versi lain (live, instrumental, karaoke) atau buatkan daftar putar singkat untukmu?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/auto","usage":{"input":91,"output":3920,"cacheRead":17280,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21291,"cost":{"input":-91,"output":-3920,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":-4011}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774458376831,"responseId":"gen-1774458377-2ACP2aQv6C6C6jXA94Di"}}
