{"type":"message","id":"09b42c4b","parentId":"0d65e84d","timestamp":"2026-03-25T17:10:32.904Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Yang paling mudah sekarang: pakai tautan YouTube langsung dan klik untuk memutar.\n\nTautan yang relevan (Risk It All - Bruno Mars):\n- https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rPpusObDFSo\n- https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BF2_ipR1OI0\n- https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lY5V4hSLWY8\n\nKalau kamu tetap ingin saya otomatis membuka browser untukmu, kita butuh konfigurasi ACP. Pilihan termudah:\n- Beri saya agentId untuk Playwright (mis. \"playwright\") dan jalankan perintah dengan itu, atau\n- Set acp.defaultAgent di konfigurasi OpenClaw ke “playwright” (lalu coba lagi), atau\n- Aktifkan runtime acpx (saya pandu langkahnya jika kamu setuju).\n\nMau saya buatkan daftar putar singkat (3–5 video) dengan versi live/instrumental/karaoke juga, atau cukup fokus pada versi resmi saja?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/auto","usage":{"input":514,"output":3165,"cacheRead":19584,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":23263,"cost":{"input":-514,"output":-3165,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":-3679}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774458617911,"responseId":"gen-1774458618-M3yaW5suq5yahoX9pQwm"}}
