{"type":"message","id":"d95b9b8c","parentId":"0a58ac2e","timestamp":"2026-03-25T17:11:45.401Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Considering user options**\n\nI can offer to run a non-browser action, like fetching a YouTube video page, even though we can't play it. I could pull the video title or description if necessary, but I should ask the user what they prefer. \n\nSince there's no tool to configure acpx, I can guide them through enabling it by accessing their machine and running some commands. First, I’d verify the installed node version, then focus on installing the acpx plugin, avoiding guesswork with commands. I can suggest high-level steps for installation and offer to queue a cron reminder to retry enabling.**Finalizing response**\n\nAlright, let's put together the final response! First, I want to acknowledge the situation and provide the three YouTube links again. I need to explain that to open a browser automatically, we'll need the ACP runtime plugin (acpx) installed and configured.\n\nI can offer a few options: (A) I can guide you through enabling acpx with exact commands once you confirm your environment; (B) You can approve fetching more links; or (C) I can try again later once you configure it.\n\nSo, do you want me to proceed with enabling acpx? If yes, I can give step-by-step instructions, or we can try a manual approach.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Saya tidak bisa membuka browser secara otomatis karena ACP runtime (acpx) belum configured. Tanpa plugin acpx, perintah open browser tidak bisa dijalankan.\n\nAlternatif cepat untuk lanjut sekarang:\n- Tautan YouTube Risk It All (klik saja untuk diputar):\n  - Bruno Mars - Risk It All [Official Music Video]: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rPpusObDFSo\n  - Bruno Mars - Risk It All [Video resmi lain]: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BF2_ipR1OI0\n  - Bruno Mars - Risk It All [Video alternatif]: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lY5V4hSLWY8\n\nOpsi untuk memungkinkan membuka browser otomatis (ACP acpx):\n- Beri saya agenId yang tepat untuk Playwright (mis. \"playwright\") dan jalankan perintah dengan itu, atau\n- Aktifkan acp.defaultAgent di konfigurasi OpenClaw ke \"playwright\" lalu coba lagi, atau\n- Set up runtime acpx (saya pandu langkahnya jika kamu setuju).\n\nLangkah panduan singkat (kalau kamu mau saya bantu):\n- Pasang dan aktifkan runtime acpx untuk OpenClaw.\n- Konfigurasikan acp.defaultAgent = \"playwright\" (atau tambahkan agentId saat spawn).\n- Restart gateway/OpenClaw jika perlu.\n- Coba lagi perintah buka browser.\n\nMau saya bantu dengan panduan langkah demi langkah untuk mengaktifkan acpx di sistem kamu, atau tetap pakai tautan langsung tadi saja?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/auto","usage":{"input":221,"output":2911,"cacheRead":20480,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":23612,"cost":{"input":-221,"output":-2911,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":-3132}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774458683921,"responseId":"gen-1774458684-mWL8noHWvuxFmY3pnQFL"}}
