{"type":"message","id":"644e01ed","parentId":"c17fdd6b","timestamp":"2026-03-25T18:00:01.585Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool_sessions_spawn_9MT2b5UpDGVvifMywyzo","toolName":"sessions_spawn","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"status\": \"error\",\n  \"error\": \"ACP runtime backend is not configured. Install and enable the acpx runtime plugin.\"\n}"}],"details":{"status":"error","error":"ACP runtime backend is not configured. Install and enable the acpx runtime plugin."},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774461601579}}
{"type":"message","id":"af28cf92","parentId":"644e01ed","timestamp":"2026-03-25T18:00:18.474Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Explaining browser limitations**\n\nWe need to respond to the user's request about using Playwright with the Brave browser to open a YouTube video in non-headless mode. We ran into an error about the acpx plugin not being configured. I should explain this constraint and suggest alternatives. I could provide steps to enable the acpx plugin, or give instructions to fetch the link and manually open Brave. It's important to ensure safety in my response and respect user privacy.**Providing instructions for users**\n\nI need to decide how to help the user. They want to play a video, but we can't do that because the acpx plugin is not configured. I could either provide them with explicit commands to run locally, or I could fetch the page and summarize it, but not play the video. I should acknowledge the issue and give them a concrete plan that includes steps to install the acpx plugin and confirm the Brave executable path.**Guiding the user on Playwright setup**\n\nIn Playwright, I'd set the `launchOptions` to `headless: false` and specify the `executablePath`. I need to configure the OpenClaw settings with `acp.defaultAgent: \"playwright\"` and then restart the gateway. If the user can't configure this, I can provide them with a direct YouTube link. It's important to remind them about the potential hazards of using acpx on Windows and ensure proper path quoting. I’ll offer a clear plan and ask them how they’d like to proceed.**Offering solutions for acpx configuration**\n\nFirst, I need to acknowledge that the acpx plugin isn't configured. I can provide the user with two options: a quick workaround with a direct YouTube link, or setup instructions for enabling acpx. I'll outline steps to install the plugin, ensure Brave can be launched by Playwright with the correct executable path, configure the acp default agent, and restart the gateway. I’ll ask if the user would like me to guide them through the exact commands for Windows or if they want me to fetch the video directly.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Maaf — perintah otomatis tidak bisa berjalan karena acpx runtime plugin belum dikonfigurasi di sistem OpenClaw kamu.\n\nRingkas rencana dua opsi:\n\nOpsi A (jalan cepat): cukup klik tautan YouTube untuk memutar video\n- Bruno Mars - Risk It All [Official Music Video]: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rPpusObDFSo\n\nOpsi B (aktifkan otomatis dengan Playwright + Brave)\nLangkah-langkah berikut untuk mengaktifkan acpx dan membuka Brave secara non-headless:\n1) Pasang plugin acpx\n- Jalankan: openclaw plugins install @openclaw/acpx\n- Atau kalau perlu, sesuaikan dengan path lokal tempat acpx berada.\n\n2) Konfigurasikan agen default ACP (untuk Playwright)\n- Edit konfigurasi OpenClaw kamu dan pastikan ada bagian:\n  {\n    \"acp\": {\n      \"defaultAgent\": \"playwright\"\n    }\n  }\n\n3) Jalankan ulang gateway/OpenClaw\n- Jalankan: openclaw gateway restart\n\n4) Jalankan perintah membuka Brave dengan Playwright\n- Contoh pola kode (di lingkungan yang mendukung Playwright):\n  - executablePath: \"C:\\\\Program Files\\\\BraveSoftware\\\\Brave-Browser\\\\Application\\\\brave.exe\"\n  - headless: false\n  - navigasi ke: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rPpusObDFSo\n\nCatatan:\n- Jalankan di Windows dengan path Brave seperti di atas; pastikan lokasi Brave yang tepat sesuai sistem kamu.\n- Jika OpenClaw kamu berada di environment yang tidak memungkinkan browser GUI, opsi A tetap paling aman.\n\nMau saya pandu langkah-demi-langkah lebih rinci dengan perintah Windows yang spesifik (termasuk contoh skrip Playwright) untuk konfigurasi ini? Atau cukup lanjutkan dengan opsi A (tautan YouTube) sekarang?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/auto","usage":{"input":20106,"output":1959,"cacheRead":3712,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTo