{"type":"message","id":"28752a0d","parentId":"518ad574","timestamp":"2026-03-25T18:23:44.989Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Evaluating options for video playback**\n\nI need to provide options for video playback. Option A is to use a direct YouTube link for manual playback. Option B involves trying to automate the process by reconnecting, like retrying after a few seconds or attempting to run a status command. However, I realize that while I have a \"gateway\" tool, the schema doesn’t support a \"status\" action. So it seems I can't programmatically check the status after all.**Outlining possible solutions**\n\nI can suggest we try again later or offer a local Playwright script that uses CDP or Brave’s debugging for a manual approach, though I can't guarantee full control. I could propose a web search to find steps for enabling acpx, but that’s already been completed. \n\nI should acknowledge the error: \"ACP runtime backend unavailable\" and outline the two paths: manually using a direct YouTube link or waiting for the ACP backend to recover. Additionally, I can provide a Node.js Playwright script for Brave to play the video, though it requires a Node environment.**Connecting Playwright to Brave**\n\nTo connect Playwright with Brave using CDP, Brave needs to be started with the remote debugging port, which we didn't set up. However, I can use Playwright's \"launch\" function, specifying Brave's executable path. Playwright supports Chromium-based browsers like Brave, so I'll pass the executable path to \"playwright.chromium.launch\" and can set it to headless: false. \n\nI have a sample script ready that opens YouTube and tries to click the play button. But I should consider that autoplay might be blocked and that the button's selector can be dynamic.**Proposing options and steps**\n\nLet’s outline the steps here. First, I’ll offer two options: \n\nOption 1 is the manual method with the YouTube link: rPpusObDFSo. \n\nOption 2 involves a local Playwright script for Brave with step-by-step guidance.\n\nI should start with an empathetic note about the unavailability of the ACP runtime backend and mention that we can try again later. I could provide a quick fallback to the YouTube link.\n\nI'll include a ready-to-run script called play_brave_risk_it_all.js, explaining it requires Node and Playwright. I'll also present steps for running it, beginning with ensuring Node.js is installed.**Preparing final response steps**\n\nI'll outline the steps for the user clearly. First, I should mention the status: ACP runtime is unavailable. \n\nThen I can provide the quick path, which is the direct link to the video for manual playback: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rPpusObDFSo.\n\nNext, I’ll mention that if they'd like, I can generate a self-contained Node.js script to use with Brave, or we can retry once it's operational again.\n\nFinally, I should ask for their preference. Okay, let’s finalize this!","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Maaf, ACP runtime (acpx) masih tidak available, jadi otomatis membuka Brave lewat Playwright belum bisa dijalankan sekarang.\n\nPilihan yang paling mudah sekarang:\n- Buka tautan video YouTube berikut dan putar secara manual:\n  - Bruno Mars - Risk It All: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rPpusObDFSo\n\nOpsi jika Anda ingin tetap otomatis (tetap butuh acpx aktif nanti):\n- Saya bisa buatkan skrip Node.js Playwright yang menjalankan Brave (executablePath) dengan headless: false, lalu navigasi ke video dan coba klik tombol Play. Anda jalankan lokal di komputer Anda setelah acpx terpasang dan Brave bisa dikontrol.\n  - Contoh ringkas skrip (sesuaikan path Brave jika diperlukan):\n    - Node.js script (play_brave_risk_it_all.js)\n    - Brave path: \"C:\\\\Program Files\\\\BraveSoftware\\\\Brave-Browser\\\\Application\\\\brave.exe\"\n    - Video: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rPpusObDFSo\n\nLangkah cepat jika Anda ingin saya buatkan skrip lengkap:\n- Saya kirimkan skrip Node.js lengkap beserta petunjuk instalasi Playwright (npm install playwright), cara menjalankannya, dan cara menangani tombol Play jika autoplay dibatasi.\n\nIngin saya lanjutkan dengan skrip Playwright lengkap untuk dijalankan di komputer Anda, atau cukup pakai tautan YouTube saja sekarang?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/auto","usage":{"input":564,"output":3050,"cacheRead":26112,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":29726,"cost":{"input":-564,"output":-3050,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":-3614}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774463002841,"responseId":"gen-1774463003-5ZPmehwxwCUXXaPGslHO"}}
{"type":"message","id":"38c2947b","parentId":"28752a0d","timestamp":"2026-03-25T18:24:37.411Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Thu 2026-03-26 01:24 GMT+7] gini bukan?\n\nPS C:\\Users\\vicor> openclaw config set acp.defaultAgent \"playwright\"\n\n🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.23-2 (7ffe7e4) — I keep secrets like a vault... unless you print them in debug logs again.\n\nConfig overwrite: C:\\Users\\vicor\\.openclaw\\openclaw.json (sha256 2db0722b1252e8baea56a8011b5b780732018cf02a68632b9fa51bea345c2b47 -> 9d04a5b49e8bc2081435c14cd8029c569c7ecb2e1429e06ece307c9883a59a2a, backup=C:\\Users\\vicor\\.openclaw\\openclaw.json.bak)\nUpdated acp.defaultAgent. Restart the gateway to apply.\nPS C:\\Users\\vicor> openclaw config set plugins.entries.playwright.config.headless false\n\n🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.23-2 (7ffe7e4) — It's not \"failing,\" it's \"discovering new ways to configure the same thing wrong.\"\n\nConfig warnings:\n- plugins.entries.playwright: plugin not found: playwright (stale config entry ignored; remove it from plugins config)\nConfig overwrite: C:\\Users\\vicor\\.openclaw\\openclaw.json (sha256 9d04a5b49e8bc2081435c14cd8029c569c7ecb2e1429e06ece307c9883a59a2a -> 2f0a24620b8d18dba016708d9d8f26875e160c126a53814d2b81061cf310c317, backup=C:\\Users\\vicor\\.openclaw\\openclaw.json.bak)\nUpdated plugins.entries.playwright.config.headless. Restart the gateway to apply.\nPS C:\\Users\\vicor>"}],"timestamp":1774463077402}}
{"type":"message","id":"f3f9dd5f","parentId":"38c2947b","timestamp":"2026-03-25T18:25:00.866Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Ringkasnya dari apa yang kamu jalankan:\n\n- Kamu sudah set acp.defaultAgent ke \"playwright\" (bagus).\n- Kamu mencoba set headless untuk Playwright via plugins.entries.playwright.config.headless, tapi plugin dengan id “playwright” tidak ditemukan di daftar plugin (entry itu usang). Artinya konfigurasi plugin Playwright yang lama harus dihapus.\n- Gateway perlu direstart agar perubahan konfigurasi diterapkan.\n\nLangkah praktis yang saya sarankan sekarang (aman dan bisa langsung dilakukan):\n\n1) Hapus entri plugin Playwright yang usang\n- Buka file konfigurasi:\n  C:\\Users\\vicor\\.openclaw\\openclaw.json\n- Cari bagian yang mengandung plugins.entries.playwright dan hapus blok itu (termasuk config.headless jika ada). Contoh yg dihapus kira-kira seperti:\n  - plugins.entries.playwright.config.headless: false\n  - atau seluruh blok plugins.entries.playwright\n\n2) Restart gateway\n- Jalankan:\n  openclaw gateway restart\n\n3) Verifikasi status ACP dan plugin\n- Cek status gateway untuk memastikan acpx (APC runtime) sudah ter-load:\n  openclaw gateway status\n- Jika perlu, cek daftar plugin:\n  openclaw plugins list\n\n4) Coba lagi buka Brave dengan Playwright (non-headless)\n- Jika acpx sudah aktif, coba spawn sesi ACP:\n  {\n    \"task\":\"Open Brave with Playwright\",\n    \"label\":\"playwright-brave\",\n    \"runtime\":\"acp\",\n    \"agentId\":\"playwright\",\n    \"resumeSessionId\":\"\",\n    \"model\":\"default\",\n    \"thinking\":\"\",\n    \"cwd\":\"\",\n    \"runTimeoutSeconds\":0,\n    \"timeoutSeconds\":0,\n    \"thread\":false,\n    \"mode\":\"run\",\n    \"cleanup\":\"delete\",\n    \"sandbox\":\"inherit\",\n    \"streamTo\":\"parent\",\n    \"attachments\":[]\n  }\n- Instruksi ini akan mencoba membuka Brave (executablePath: \"C:\\Program Files\\BraveSoftware\\Brave-Browser\\Application\\brave.exe\") dalam non-headless dan navigasi ke video YouTube.\n\nAlternatif jika ingin langsung tanpa langkah konfigurasi:\n- Jika kamu tidak bisa menunggu konfigurasi, kita tetap bisa pakai tautan YouTube untuk diputar manual:\n  - Bruno Mars - Risk It All: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rPpusObDFSo\n\nIngin saya buatkan panduan langkah demi langkah (dengan skrip PowerShell/Node.js Playwright) yang bisa kamu jalankan lokal untuk otomatis membuka Brave dan memutar video begitu acpx sudah aktif? Atau kita lanjut dulu dengan langkah konfigurasi di atas dan verifikasi statusnya?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/auto","usage":{"input":27473,"output":4204,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31677,"cost":{"input":-27473,"output":-4204,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":-31677}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774463077429,"responseId":"gen-1774463078-1jL4JcnMocY5l4sud8PA"}}
{"type":"message","id":"bdcff112","parentId":"f3f9dd5f","timestamp":"2026-03-25T18:25:52.733Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Thu 2026-03-26 01:25 GMT+7] gini?\n\n{\n \"meta\": {\n \"lastTouchedVersion\": \"2026.3.23-2\",\n \"lastTouchedAt\": \"2026-03-25T18:22:32.767Z\"\n },\n \"wizard\": {\n \"lastRunAt\": \"2026-03-25T16:25:06.067Z\",\n \"lastRunVersion\": \"2026.3.23-2\",\n \"lastRunCommand\": \"configure\",\n \"lastRunMode\": \"local\"\n },\n \"browser\": {\n \"executablePath\": \"C:\\\\Program Files\\\\BraveSoftware\\\\Brave-Browser\\\\Application\\\\brave.exe\"\n },\n \"auth\": {\n \"profiles\": {\n \"openrouter:default\": {\n \"provider\": \"openrouter\",\n \"mode\": \"api_key\"\n }\n }\n },\n \"acp\": {\n \"defaultAgent\": \"playwright\"\n },\n \"agents\": {\n \"defaults\": {\n \"model\": {\n \"primary\": \"openrouter/auto\"\n },\n \"models\": {\n \"openrouter/anthropic/claude-3.5-sonnet\": {}\n },\n \"workspace\": \"C:\\\\Users\\\\vicor\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\",\n \"compaction\": {\n \"mode\": \"safeguard\"\n }\n },\n \"list\": [\n {\n \"id\": \"main\",\n \"tools\": {\n \"profile\": \"full\",\n \"alsoAllow\": [\n \"browser\",\n \"tavily_search\",\n \"tavily_extract\"\n ]\n }\n }\n ]\n },\n \"tools\": {\n \"profile\": \"coding\",\n \"web\": {\n \"search\": {\n \"enabled\": true,\n \"provider\": \"tavily\"\n }\n }\n },\n \"commands\": {\n \"native\": \"auto\",\n \"nativeSkills\": \"auto\",\n \"restart\": true,\n \"ownerDisplay\": \"raw\"\n },\n \"session\": {\n \"dmScope\": \"per-channel-peer\"\n },\n \"gateway\": {\n \"port\": 18789,\n \"mode\": \"local\",\n \"bind\": \"loopback\",\n \"auth\": {\n \"mode\": \"token\",\n \"token\": \"1c1e48f6f893146f53c8bb64ef4fbc13c217c0b61e7ecf62\"\n },\n \"tailscale\": {\n \"mode\": \"off\",\n \"resetOnExit\": false\n }\n },\n \"skills\": {\n \"install\": {\n \"nodeM