ns] acpx runtime backend registered (command: C:\\Users\\vicor\\AppData\\Roaming\\nvm\\v22.22.0\\node_modules\\openclaw\\dist\\extensions\\acpx\\node_modules\\.bin\\acpx.cmd, expectedVersion: 0.3.1, pluginLocalInstall: enabled)\n01:26:31 [plugins] acpx local binary unavailable or mismatched (acpx.cmd wrapper resolved, but no executable/Node entrypoint could be resolved without shell execution.); running plugin-local install\n01:26:31 [ws] webchat connected conn=84cd2d18-efa7-4ad2-9d9c-e754effd8308 remote=127.0.0.1 client=openclaw-control-ui webchat v2026.3.23-2\n01:26:31 [plugins] acpx runtime setup failed: plugin-local acpx verification failed after install: acpx.cmd wrapper resolved, but no executable/Node entrypoint could be resolved without shell execution.\n01:26:31 [ws] ⇄ res ✓ node.list 212ms conn=84cd2d18…8308 id=a0f8b516…ba29\n01:26:31 [ws] ⇄ res ✓ device.pair.list 219ms conn=84cd2d18…8308 id=4b21544f…de37\n01:26:33 [ws] ⇄ res ✓ chat.history 1628ms conn=84cd2d18…8308 id=c5003420…c3f2\n01:26:33 [ws] ⇄ res ✓ models.list 1592ms conn=84cd2d18…8308 id=a87ffcb4…8b09"}],"timestamp":1774463225701}}
{"type":"message","id":"af716be8","parentId":"86207c32","timestamp":"2026-03-25T18:27:26.582Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Interpreting user log findings**\n\nI need to respond to the user’s lengthy log snippet that shows config warnings and issues with the acpx plugin. They previously asked about running Playwright to open Brave, but there’s a runtime backend problem. I see warnings about the playwright plugin being a stale config entry that should be removed, and about the acpx runtime setup failing too. I should give them a concise diagnostic and suggest they remove the misconfigured \"playwright\" plugin entry.**Diagnosing acpx issues**\n\nThe log indicates that acpx is installed, but there's a problem with the local binary being unavailable or mismatched, which means it’s not working properly. The user wants to open Brave using Playwright, but we need acpx functioning to connect to Brave's executable. We must ensure the acpx binary exists in the specified path, but right now it’s missing. To address this, I should suggest cleaning up the config by removing the Playwright block entirely and relying on the acpx runtime.**Proposing troubleshooting steps**\n\nI need to ensure acpx is the runtime plugin loaded and that the binary is correct. I can suggest running \"openclaw gateway restart\" to reload and check the acpx version from the logs. It’s worth proposing an update to the latest plugin version and reinstalling acpx using \"openclaw plugins install acpx.\" I should also verify acpx is listed and enabled by running \"openclaw plugins list.\" If issues persist, I may have to provide alternative solutions, and I should ask for permission to pursue advanced steps or proceed manually.**Reviewing safety and formatting**\n\nI need to ensure there are no policy issues involved. While I should keep formatting light, using a bullet list is acceptable. I also shouldn't call any tools unless absolutely necessary. I plan to read the log and suggest actionable steps. For Step A, I’ll provide clear instructions to remove the stale Playwright plugin entries from the config. Specifically, I’ll instruct the user to modify the C:\\Users\\vicor\\.openclaw\\openclaw.json file to remove the \"entries.playwright\" block.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Terima kasih. Dari log terbaru, ada dua isu utama:\n\n- Plugin Playwright terkonfigurasi sebagai entri “usang” (stale) sehingga memberi peringatan “plugin not found: playwright” meski acpx sudah ada.\n- ACPCX runtime masih gagal: binary lokal acpx belum terdeteksi dengan benar, sehingga membuka Brave via Playwright belum bisa berjalan.\n\nRencana singkat untuk lanjut (aman dan jelas):\n\n1) Bersihkan entri plugin Playwright yang usang\n- Buka file:\n  C:\\Users\\vicor\\.openclaw\\openclaw.json\n- Hapus blok entri untuk Playwright di bawah plugins.entries, seperti:\n  \"playwright\": {\n    \"config\": {\n      \"headless\": false\n    }\n  }\n- Simpan perubahan.\n\n2) Restart gateway agar perubahan diterapkan\n- Jalankan:\n  openclaw gateway restart\n\n3) Verifikasi status ACP dan plugin\n- Cek status gateway:\n  openclaw gateway status\n- Cek daftar plugin:\n  openclaw plugins list\n\n4) Cek kembali kemampuan ACPCX\n- Pastikan acpx ter-load dengan benar dan tidak lagi mengeluarkan error “plugin-local acpx verification failed”.\n- Jika masih ada error, kita mungkin perlu reinstall acpx atau menyesuaikan path binary.\n\n5) Coba lagi menjalankan Brave via Playwright\n- Jika ACPCX sudah oke, saya bisa bantu kirim perintah/mode spawn untuk:\n  - Brave executablePath: \"C:\\Program Files\\BraveSoftware\\Brave-Browser\\Application\\brave.exe\"\n  - headless: false\n  - navigasi ke: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rPpusObDFSo\n  - dan mencoba memulai pemutaran video (klik Play jika autoplay dibatasi)\n\nAlternatif cepat kalau ingin tidak menunggu konfigurasi:\n- Gunakan tautan YouTube langsung untuk memutar video:\n  - Bruno Mars - Risk It All: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rPpusObDFSo\n\nMau saya lanjutkan dengan langkah 1 (hapus entri Playwright dan restart gateway) sekarang? Jika ya, saya bisa mengarahkan langkah per langkahnya atau membantu mengeluarkan perintah yang tepat untuk patch file secara otomatis."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/auto","usage":{"input":2858,"output":3702,"cacheRead":27392,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":33952,"cost":{"input":-2858,"output":-3702,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":-6560}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774463225883,"responseId":"gen-1774463226-NDSnuejbFh9OwRwEjmkh"}}
