{"type":"message","id":"7e89e812","parentId":"e8a8cc25","timestamp":"2026-03-25T18:31:10.510Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Proposing alternatives for Playwright usage**\n\nI’m considering different options for running a local Playwright script that connects to Brave using CDP. The first step is to close Brave and then start it with the debugging port enabled. Next, I’ll write a Node.js script that connects over CDP to the correct URL. I’ll also provide a simple script snippet and installation instructions. \n\nAlternatively, I can offer to revert to a manual solution using direct YouTube links or creating a playlist, making sure to keep everything concise and actionable for the user.**Suggesting actions for user**\n\nI’m considering how to help the user with their request regarding opening Brave and playing a Bruno Mars video. \n\nFirst, I can suggest they wait and retry after a brief pause. Alternatively, I could provide a direct link to the video for a manual approach. If they prefer automation, I would propose steps to enable the CDP connection, ensuring they launch Brave with the correct debugging port and offering a Playwright script for connecting. I should ask them to choose which path they prefer.**Crafting options for user**\n\nI need to start with a brief status update: the ACP runtime is currently unavailable, but the gateway restart was successful, so I'm trying again. \n\nI can provide a few options for the user: \n\nOption A is to keep trying in the background and request permission to retry in a few minutes. Option B suggests a manual approach they can take. Option C offers a ready-to-run Node script with instructions for installing dependencies. \n\nI should also acknowledge the current failure while giving three clear options for how to proceed.**Providing automation options**\n\nIf the user wants automation right now, I can give them a self-contained Node.js script along with steps to enable the CDP connection in Brave using the debugging port. \n\nI should mention that I will attempt to connect automatically again in about a minute. I can also reassure them that the YouTube video URL is still available. It’s important to keep everything clear and actionable for the user while ensuring I don’t use any tools at this point.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Singkatnya: saat ini ACP runtime (acpx) masih belum tersedia. Gateway sudah direstart, namun backend acpx belum siap sehingga perintah otomatis membuka Brave melalui Playwright gagal.\n\nPilihan untuk lanjut, sesuaikan kenyamananmu:\n\n- Opsi A — coba lagi otomatis nanti\n  - Aku bisa mencoba lagi secara otomatis beberapa menit ke depan dan mengabari hasilnya. Beri tahu aku berapa lama waktu tunggu yang kamu inginkan (contoh: 60 detik, 2 menit).\n\n- Opsi B — lanjut manual sekarang\n  - Buka Brave secara manual dan navigasi ke video:\n    - Bruno Mars - Risk It All: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rPpusObDFSo\n  - Putar videonya secara manual. Jika autoplay dibatasi, klik tombol Play.\n\n- Opsi C — panduan otomatis menggunakan CDP (tanpa acpx)\n  Jika kamu ingin otomatis sekarang, kita bisa pakai pendekatan alternatif dengan Chrome DevTools Protocol (CDP):\n  1) Tutup Brave dulu.\n  2) Jalankan Brave dengan remote debugging port:\n     - brave.exe --remote-debugging-port=9222\n  3) Gunakan Playwright untuk terhubung via CDP:\n     - Contoh Node.js (jalankan di mesinmu):\n       - Install Playwright: npm i playwright\n       - Jalankan skrip:\n         const { chromium } = require('playwright');\n         (async () => {\n           const browser = await chromium.connectOverCDP('http://localhost:9222');\n           const pages = await browser.pages();\n           const page = pages.length ? pages[0] : await browser.newPage();\n           await page.goto('https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rPpusObDFSo', { waitUntil: 'networkidle' });\n           // Jika autoplay tidak langsung, coba klik Play\n           // await page.click('button[aria-label=\"Play\"]');\n         })();\n  4) Catatan: autoplay di YouTube sering dibatasi browser; kemungkinan perlu klik Play secara manual.\n\nBeritahu saya opsi mana yang mau kamu pakai. Jika kamu pilih Opsi A, aku akan mencoba lagi otomatis dalam beberapa menit dan kasih tahu hasilnya. Jika kamu pilih Opsi C, aku akan memberi skrip lengkap dan langkah-langkah persiapan yang lebih terperinci."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/auto","usage":{"input":274,"output":2674,"cacheRead":33408,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":36356,"cost":{"input":-274,"output":-2674,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":-2948}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774463439334,"responseId":"gen-1774463439-HGWJxNCUJvbXaqcHLiNL"}}
